---
title: Spicy Sweetcorn Curry with rice and roasted potatoes
description: Curry with a kick! This veg-packed dish is healthy with plenty of heat. Rogan josh paste, North Indian spice mix and fresh chilli all combine to make a spicy dish that you won't want to miss.
